" More readable on a black background than default
colorscheme desert
syntax on
set autoindent

filetype plugin indent on


" Masochistic anti-arrow-key settings.
"noremap  <Up> ""
"noremap! <Up> <Esc>
"noremap  <Down> ""
"noremap! <Down> <Esc>
"noremap  <Left> ""
"noremap! <Left> <Esc>
"noremap  <Right> ""
"noremap! <Right> <Esc>
" Less masochsitic anti-PgUp/PgDown
noremap  <PageUp> ""
noremap! <PageUp> <Esc>
noremap <PageDown> ""
noremap! <PageDown> <Esc>
